<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    font-size: 11pt;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 20mm 20mm 20mm 20mm;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #dc2626;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .school-info h2 { font-size: 15pt; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .school-info p  { font-size: 9pt; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.6; }
  .logo { max-height: 60px; max-width: 160px; object-fit: contain; }
  h1 {
    font-size: 16pt;
    text-align: center;
    color: #dc2626;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }
  .doc-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 10pt;
    color: #64748b;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 10pt;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #dc2626;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #fecaca;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    margin: 20px 0 10px;
  }
  table.info { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  table.info td {
    padding: 5px 8px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    font-size: 10pt;
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  table.info td:first-child {
    font-weight: bold;
    background: #f8fafc;
    width: 38%;
    color: #334155;
  }
  .incident-box {
    border: 2px solid #dc2626;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    background: #fef2f2;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .incident-box p { font-size: 10pt; line-height: 1.7; white-space: pre-wrap; }
  .cost-box {
    background: #fff7ed;
    border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 10pt;
  }
  .sig-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 30px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .sig-block { flex: 1; }
  .sig-line {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
    height: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .sig-label { font-size: 9pt; color: #64748b; }
  .footer {
    margin-top: 24px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 8pt;
    color: #94a3b8;
    border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    padding-top: 8px;
  }
  .warning-header {
    background: #fee2e2;
    border: 1px solid #fca5a5;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 10pt;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #991b1b;
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
  <div class="school-info">
    <h2>{{settings.school_name}}</h2>
    <p>
      {{#if settings.school_address}}{{settings.school_address}}<br />{{/if}}
      {{#if settings.school_city}}{{settings.school_city}}<br />{{/if}}
      {{#if settings.school_phone}}Tel.: {{settings.school_phone}}<br />{{/if}}
      {{#if settings.school_email}}{{settings.school_email}}{{/if}}
    </p>
  </div>
  {{#if settings.logo}}
    <img class="logo" src="{{settings.logo}}" alt="Schullogo" />
  {{/if}}
</div>

<h1>{{report.type_label}}</h1>
<p class="doc-subtitle">Meldung eines Schadens oder Verlustes an einem schuleigenen iPad</p>

<div class="warning-header">
  {{#if report.is_verlust}}
    VERLUSTMELDUNG &ndash; Das iPad wurde als verloren gemeldet.
  {{else}}
    DEFEKTMELDUNG &ndash; Das iPad wurde als defekt gemeldet.
  {{/if}}
</div>

<div class="section-title">Daten des Ausleihenden</div>
<table class="info">
  <tr><td>Name</td><td>{{student.last_name}}, {{student.first_name}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Klasse</td><td>{{student.class}}</td></tr>
  {{#if student.moin_username}}
  <tr><td>Moin.Schule-Benutzername</td><td>{{student.moin_username}}</td></tr>
  {{/if}}
  {{#if student.guardian_email}}
  <tr><td>E-Mail (Erziehungsberechtigte)</td><td>{{student.guardian_email}}</td></tr>
  {{/if}}
  {{#if student.guardian_phone}}
  <tr><td>Telefon (Erziehungsberechtigte)</td><td>{{student.guardian_phone}}</td></tr>
  {{/if}}
</table>

<div class="section-title">Daten des iPads</div>
<table class="info">
  <tr><td>iPad-Nummer</td><td><strong>{{ipad.asset_tag}}</strong></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Modell</td><td>{{ipad.model}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Seriennummer</td><td style="font-family:monospace">{{ipad.serial}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Ausleihdatum</td><td>{{ipad.lent_date}}</td></tr>
</table>

<div class="section-title">Meldung</div>
<table class="info" style="margin-bottom:10px">
  <tr><td>Meldedatum</td><td>{{report.report_date_formatted}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Art</td><td><strong>{{report.type_label}}</strong></td></tr>
</table>

<div class="incident-box">
  <strong>Beschreibung:</strong>
  <p>{{report.description}}</p>
</div>

{{#if report.repair_cost}}
<div class="cost-box">
  <strong>Geschätzte Reparatur- / Wiederbeschaffungskosten:</strong> {{report.repair_cost_formatted}}
</div>
{{/if}}

<p style="margin-top:16px;font-size:10pt">
Mit der Unterschrift wird bestätigt, dass der oben beschriebene Sachverhalt der Wahrheit entspricht.
Bei Verlust oder grob fahrlässiger Beschädigung können Kosten geltend gemacht werden.
</p>

<div class="section-title">Unterschriften</div>
<div class="sig-row">
  <div class="sig-block">
    <div class="sig-line"></div>
    <div class="sig-label">Datum, Unterschrift Schüler/in</div>
  </div>
  <div class="sig-block">
    <div class="sig-line"></div>
    <div class="sig-label">Datum, Unterschrift Erziehungsberechtigte/r</div>
  </div>
  <div class="sig-block">
    <div class="sig-line"></div>
    <div class="sig-label">Stempel &amp; Unterschrift Schule</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  Erstellt am {{created_date}} &bull; {{settings.school_name}}
</div>

</body>
</html>
